OL,3,CVictims of cockling disaster
OL,4,Cremembered 20 years on
OL,6,FA plea for "a kinder society" has been
OL,7,Fmade as the 20th anniversary of the
OL,8,FMorecambe Bay cockling tragedy was
OL,9,Fmarked.
OL,11,FPeople gathered to remember the 23
OL,12,Fpeople who drowned after becoming
OL,13,Ftrapped by the tide when they were
OL,14,Fforced to work by their Chinese
OL,15,Fgangmaster.
OL,17,FOn West End Beach braziers and
OL,18,Flanterns were lit and there were
OL,19,Fmusical performances.
