OL,3,CVictims of cockling disaster
OL,4,Cremembered 20 years on
OL,6,FIt was one of a number of events to
OL,7,Fcommemorate the anniversary.
OL,9,FCommunity musician and organiser Peter
OL,10,FMoser said: "It's a time to remember
OL,11,Fthose people and think about how we
OL,12,Fcan change things so it doesn't happen
OL,13,Fagain.
OL,15,F"The trafficking will go on. But it's
OL,16,Fnot just trafficking that puts people
OL,17,Finto danger.
