OL,3,CVictims of cockling disaster
OL,4,Cremembered 20 years on
OL,6,F"We need somehow to make a kinder
OL,7,Fsociety, where people care for each
OL,8,Fother and where there are
OL,9,Fopportunities to work legally and find
OL,10,Fways to contribute to their
OL,11,Fcommunities."
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of a service of vigil
OL,14,Fand remembrance to mark the
OL,15,Fanniversary, the Rector of Morecambe
OL,16,FParish Church, Rev. Chris Krawiec
OL,17,Fsaid: "At times like these it's
OL,18,Fimportant to come together as a
OL,19,Fcommunity, itself made up of different
OL,20,Fcommunities, to acknowledge and
OL,21,Fremember.
