OL,3,CVictims of cockling disaster
OL,4,Cremembered 20 years on
OL,6,F"As we do so we also consider how, 20
OL,7,Fyears on, trafficking and modern
OL,8,Fslavery remains huge problem and we
OL,9,Fcontinue to call for change and action
OL,10,Fto bring the scourge of modern slavery
OL,11,Fto an end."
OL,13,FThe service will include a reading of
OL,14,Fthe names of those who died. People
OL,15,Fattending will be offered a cockle
OL,16,Fshell to take away as a permanent
OL,17,Freminder of those who died.
